（參考章節：2.2.2）', '{"A": "A. (i),(ii),(iii)", "B": "B. (ii),(iii),(iv)", "C": "C. (i),(iii),(iv)", "D": "D. (i),(ii),(iii),(iv)"}', 'D', 110, '2026-02-21 13:44:45.211355+00'),
