	('3bd7c69f-594f-44af-9746-dc6aa9e55f3e', 'e8d73d9c-8262-429b-a357-7d314aa64436', 'plan_020bd566-6d94-421d-9bcd-d018ed', 0, '[{"id": "03750cd5-f6d7-4e3d-94f4-8019ccbac650", "tags": [], "set_id": "c070b487-ae96-4715-a9d0-b20949c74f1d", "choices": ["A. 船隻沉沒", "B. 買入公司股票", "C. 建築物因恐怖襲擊而被摧毀", "D. 一幅名貴的畫於博物館被盜"], "image_url": null, "created_at": "2026-02-19T12:57:59.034071+00:00", "difficulty": "medium", "updated_at": "2026-02-19T12:57:59.034071+00:00", "explanation": "", "order_index": 18, "question_text": "19. 以下哪項不是「純粹風險」？（參考章節：1.1.2a）", "correct_answer_index": 1}, {"id": "d93dbfb2-70a0-4251-a6cb-d13ed296fa73", "tags": [], "set_id": "c070b487-ae96-4715-a9d0-b20949c74f1d", "choices": ["A. 它相當可能涉及損失，不會出現收益", "B. 它只影響個人而非整體社會", "C. 根據定義，它的影響並非災難性的", "D. 它相當可能是不可保的"], "image_url": null, "created_at": "2026-02-19T12:57:59.034071+00:00", "difficulty": "medium", "updated_at": "2026-02-19T12:57:59.034071+00:00", "explanation": "", "order_index": 19, "question_text": "20. 以下哪項正確地描述「基本風險」？（參考章節：1.1.2b）", "correct_answer_index": 3}, {"id": "422fd984-0672-407d-88ad-f46cb2ed476c", "tags": [], "set_id": "c070b487-ae96-4715-a9d0-b20949c74f1d", "choices": ["A. 都是可保的", "B. 都是不可保的", "C. 通常是可保的", "D. 只適用於個人而非公司風險"], "image_url": null, "created_at": "2026-02-19T12:57:59.034071+00:00", "difficulty": "medium", "updated_at": "2026-02-19T12:57:59.034071+00:00", "explanation": "", "order_index": 20, "question_text": "21. 特定風險：（參考章節：1.1.2b）", "correct_answer_index": 2}, {"id": "65370732-7adc-4d04-a68f-efe243ae4bdf", "tags": [], "set_id": "c070b487-ae96-4715-a9d0-b20949c74f1d", "choices": ["A. 風險避免", "B. 損失防範", "C. 損失降低", "D. 風險融資"], "image_url": null, "created_at": "2026-02-19T12:57:59.034071+00:00", "difficulty": "medium", "updated_at": "2026-02-19T12:57:59.034071+00:00", "explanation": "", "order_index": 21, "question_text": "22. 「安裝自動灑水系統」是以下哪項處理風險的方法？（參考章節：1.1.3）", "correct_answer_index": 2}, {"id": "71d71e0e-7270-4978-b11e-360c90d63b3e", "tags": [], "set_id": "c070b487-ae96-4715-a9d0-b20949c74f1d", "choices": ["A. 屬於保險學的其中一部分", "B. 它只適用於純粹風險", "C. 它的三大步驟為風險免除、風險轉換及權益投資", "D. 它包含風險的識別與應付"], "image_url": null, "created_at": "2026-02-19T12:57:59.034071+00:00", "difficulty": "medium", "updated_at": "2026-02-19T12:57:59.034071+00:00", "explanation": "", "order_index": 22, "question_text": "23. 「風險管理」一詞正確描述為：（參考章節：1.1.3）", "correct_answer_index": 3}, {"id": "407aeac8-6d77-461c-8887-494d063f64c6", "tags": [], "set_id": "c070b487-ae96-4715-a9d0-b20949c74f1d", "choices": ["A. 只有 i, ii, iii", "B. 只有 ii, iii, iv", "C. 只有 i, ii, iv", "D. i, ii, iii, iv"], "image_url": null, "created_at": "2026-02-19T12:57:59.034071+00:00", "difficulty": "medium", "updated_at": "2026-02-19T12:57:59.034071+00:00", "explanation": "", "order_index": 23, "question_text": "24. 以下哪項有關風險管理的陳述是正確的？\n(i) 風險管理一詞可與純粹風險及投機風險有關\n(ii) 保險人相當可能將範圍收窄至純粹風險\n(iii) 投資者相當可能將範圍收窄至投機風險\n(iv) 保險公司較注重如何降低受保風險的手段\n（參考章節：1.1.3）", "correct_answer_index": 3}, {"id": "3cb37dc2-2e83-4fac-a66b-64df341aa836", "tags": [], "set_id": "c070b487-ae96-4715-a9d0-b20949c74f1d", "choices": ["A. 保險人通常會廣義地應用這個詞彙", "B. 在投資的術語中，這通常涉及投機風險", "C. 保險人有時把這個範圍收窄至只對可保風險的管理", "D. 風險管理的應用可以包括投機風險和純粹風險"], "image_url": null, "created_at": "2026-02-19T12:57:59.034071+00:00", "difficulty": "medium", "updated_at": "2026-02-19T12:57:59.034071+00:00", "explanation": "", "order_index": 24, "question_text": "25. 以下哪一項有關風險管理的說明是不正確的？（參考章節：1.1.3）", "correct_answer_index": 0}, {"id": "34fab984-408e-42b3-b90a-3487b3f5efb9", "tags": [], "set_id": "c070b487-ae96-4715-a9d0-b20949c74f1d", "choices": ["A. 保險是風險管理其中一環", "B. 風險管理是保險管理其中一環", "C. 保險和風險是完全相同的學科", "D. 保險和風險是沒有相似之處的"], "image_url": null, "created_at": "2026-02-19T12:57:59.034071+00:00", "difficulty": "medium", "updated_at": "2026-02-19T12:57:59.034071+00:00", "explanation": "", "order_index": 25, "question_text": "26. 以下哪項是正確的？（參考章節：1.1.3）", "correct_answer_index": 0}, {"id": "47818e00-9470-4c4b-afcb-5a6a3ae458a8", "tags": [], "set_id": "c070b487-ae96-4715-a9d0-b20949c74f1d", "choices": ["A. 是保險的其中一環", "B. 只處理投機風險", "C. 包含保險作為其中一種應付的工具", "D. 與保險沒有關係"], "image_url": null, "created_at": "2026-02-19T12:57:59.034071+00:00", "difficulty": "medium", "updated_at": "2026-02-19T12:57:59.034071+00:00", "explanation": "", "order_index": 26, "question_text": "27. 作為一門獨立的學科，風險管理：（參考章節：1.1.3）", "correct_answer_index": 2}, {"id": "ac4ddd75-de55-4edd-866d-45713ebeac9f", "tags": [], "set_id": "c070b487-ae96-4715-a9d0-b20949c74f1d", "choices": ["A. 只是保險學科的其中一環", "B. 只涉及可保風險", "C. 只涉及在本質上屬於投機性的風險", "D. 可被形容為包括保險為其中一項可供採用的方法"], "image_url": null, "created_at": "2026-02-19T12:57:59.034071+00:00", "difficulty": "medium", "updated_at": "2026-02-19T12:57:59.034071+00:00", "explanation": "", "order_index": 27, "question_text": "28. 作為一個獨立的學科，風險管理：（參考章節：1.1.3）", "correct_answer_index": 3}]', '[]', '2026-03-05 15:53:15.686+00', '2026-03-08 05:35:34.933074+00', false);
